---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import SiteHeader from '../components/SiteHeader.astro';
import SiteFooter from '../components/SiteFooter.astro';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
const R2 = 'https://dl.voltui.io/latest';
const repo = 'https://github.com/zuohuadong/volt-gui';

let goVer = '1.17';
try {
  const r = await fetch(`${R2}/latest.json`);
  if (r.ok) { const d = await r.json(); goVer = String(d.version || '').replace(/^v/, '') || goVer; }
} catch {}
---
<Base
  title="Docs — VoltUI"
  titleEn="Docs — VoltUI"
  titleZh="文档 — VoltUI"
  bodyClass="docs-page"
  description="Install VoltUI, start your first session, configure DeepSeek, and understand the prefix-cache loop. CLI commands, slash commands, MCP plugins, permissions and sandbox.">

  <SiteHeader active="docs" />

  <main class="docs-layout">
    <aside class="docs-side">
      <div class="side-group">
        <span class="gh"><span class="l-en">Getting started</span><span class="l-zh">快速开始</span></span>
        <a href="#install"><span class="l-en">Installation</span><span class="l-zh">安装</span></a>
        <a href="#quickstart"><span class="l-en">Quick start</span><span class="l-zh">快速上手</span></a>
        <a href="#config"><span class="l-en">Configuration</span><span class="l-zh">配置</span></a>
        <a href="#offline"><span class="l-en">Enterprise offline</span><span class="l-zh">企业离线准备</span></a>
      </div>
      <div class="side-group">
        <span class="gh"><span class="l-en">Concepts</span><span class="l-zh">核心概念</span></span>
        <a href="#cache"><span class="l-en">Prefix cache</span><span class="l-zh">前缀缓存</span></a>
        <a href="#permissions"><span class="l-en">Permissions &amp; sandbox</span><span class="l-zh">权限与沙箱</span></a>
        <a href="#mcp"><span class="l-en">Plugins (MCP)</span><span class="l-zh">插件(MCP)</span></a>
      </div>
      <div class="side-group">
        <span class="gh"><span class="l-en">Reference</span><span class="l-zh">参考</span></span>
        <a href="#usage"><span class="l-en">Usage report</span><span class="l-zh">用量报表</span></a>
        <a href="#cli"><span class="l-en">CLI &amp; slash commands</span><span class="l-zh">命令行与斜杠命令</span></a>
        <a href="#configfile"><span class="l-en">Config file</span><span class="l-zh">配置文件</span></a>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <article class="docs-main">
      <h1><span class="l-en">Documentation</span><span class="l-zh">文档</span></h1>
      <p class="lede"><span class="l-en">Everything you need to install VoltUI, start your first session, and understand why long sessions stay cheap. For the full engineering contract, see the <a href={`${repo}/blob/main/docs/SPEC.md`}>Spec</a> and <a href={`${repo}/blob/main/docs/GUIDE.md`}>Guide</a> on GitHub.</span><span class="l-zh">从安装到第一次会话,以及理解为什么长会话依然便宜——你需要的都在这里。完整工程契约见 GitHub 上的 <a href={`${repo}/blob/main/docs/SPEC.md`}>Spec</a> 与 <a href={`${repo}/blob/main/docs/GUIDE.md`}>Guide</a>。</span></p>

      <h2 id="install"><span class="l-en">Installation</span><span class="l-zh">安装</span></h2>
      <p><span class="l-en">One command on macOS, Linux, Windows, or WSL.</span><span class="l-zh">一条命令,支持 macOS、Linux、Windows 或 WSL。</span></p>
      <pre class="codeblock"><button data-copy="npm i -g voltui@next">Copy</button><span class="c"># npm (Go 1.x · recommended · 推荐)</span>
npm i -g voltui@next

<span class="c"># Homebrew</span>
brew install esengine/voltui/voltui</pre>
      <div class="callout"><span class="ico">!</span><span><span class="l-en">The npm <code>latest</code> tag is pinned at <strong>v0.53</strong> — a deprecated line that no longer receives updates. All 1.x releases (currently <strong>v{goVer}</strong>, a single Go binary with no Node runtime) ship on <code>@next</code>.</span><span class="l-zh">npm 的 <code>latest</code> 标签固定在 <strong>v0.53</strong>——该线已废弃、不再更新。所有 1.x 版本(当前 <strong>v{goVer}</strong>,单 Go 二进制、无需 Node)均发布在 <code>@next</code> 渠道。</span></span></div>
      <p><span class="l-en">Prefer a GUI? Desktop apps for macOS, Windows, and Linux are on the <a href={`${base}/#top`}>download page</a>.</span><span class="l-zh">想用图形界面?macOS、Windows、Linux 桌面端请前往<a href={`${base}/#top`}>下载页</a>。</span></p>

      <h2 id="offline"><span class="l-en">Enterprise offline preparation</span><span class="l-zh">企业离线准备</span></h2>
      <p><span class="l-en">Public npm, Homebrew and release downloads are convenient acquisition paths, not requirements for an enterprise runtime. For a private or air-gapped network, administrators should acquire and verify artifacts in a connected preparation zone, then distribute them through an internal software repository, endpoint manager or approved offline media.</span><span class="l-zh">公网 npm、Homebrew 与 Release 下载是便捷的获取方式，不是企业运行时要求。对于内网或隔离网络，管理员应在联网准备区获取并校验制品，再通过内部软件仓库、终端管理系统或获批离线介质分发。</span></p>
      <div class="offline-doc-grid">
        <article><strong>CLI / TUI</strong><p><span class="l-en">Distribute the platform-specific Go binary plus reviewed configuration. The CLI does not require Node at runtime.</span><span class="l-zh">分发对应平台的 Go 二进制与经审查配置；CLI 运行时不需要 Node。</span></p></article>
        <article><strong>Wails Desktop</strong><p><span class="l-en">Distribute the built desktop application and validate platform WebView requirements, signing and your upgrade path.</span><span class="l-zh">分发已构建的桌面应用，并验证平台 WebView 依赖、签名与升级路径。</span></p></article>
      </div>
      <p><span class="l-en">Prepare provider templates, credential injection, permissions, approved MCP servers and any required executables before rollout. Do not hardcode credentials in packages.</span><span class="l-zh">部署前准备 Provider 模板、凭据注入、权限、已批准的 MCP 服务及其所需可执行文件。不要在软件包中硬编码凭据。</span></p>
      <div class="callout"><span class="ico">i</span><span><span class="l-en"><strong>CodeGraph is optional.</strong> It downloads an external runtime on first use in a connected environment. Offline deployments must install or pre-cache that runtime in advance; VoltUI's core repository workflow does not require CodeGraph.</span><span class="l-zh"><strong>CodeGraph 是可选能力。</strong> 在联网环境中首次使用会下载外部运行时；离线部署必须提前安装或预缓存。VoltUI 的核心代码库工作流不依赖 CodeGraph。</span></span></div>

      <h2 id="quickstart"><span class="l-en">Quick start</span><span class="l-zh">快速上手</span></h2>
      <p><span class="l-en">First run is minimal — <code>voltui setup</code> walks you through picking a provider and keys. Then point VoltUI at a repo and start a session:</span><span class="l-zh">首次运行很简单——<code>voltui setup</code> 引导你选择 provider 与密钥。然后指向仓库、开始会话:</span></p>
      <pre class="codeblock"><button data-copy="cd your-project && voltui code">Copy</button>cd your-project
voltui code</pre>
      <p><span class="l-en">Then just describe the task:</span><span class="l-zh">然后直接描述任务:</span></p>
      <pre class="codeblock"><span class="a">›</span> add retry with backoff to the http client
<span class="a">›</span> refactor the auth flow, keep the public API stable
<span class="a">›</span> why is the worker leaking memory?</pre>
      <p><span class="l-en">Leave the session running — context is append-only, so every new turn starts from a cache hit instead of a cold start.</span><span class="l-zh">让会话一直跑着——上下文只追加,每一轮都从缓存命中开始,而不是冷启动。</span></p>

      <h2 id="config"><span class="l-en">Configuration</span><span class="l-zh">配置</span></h2>
      <p><span class="l-en">VoltUI connects to OpenAI-compatible or Anthropic endpoints with your own credentials. Secrets come from the environment via <code>api_key_env</code> and are never written to config files:</span><span class="l-zh">VoltUI 使用你自己的凭据连接 OpenAI 兼容或 Anthropic 端点。密钥通过 <code>api_key_env</code> 从环境读取，绝不写入配置文件：</span></p>
      <pre class="codeblock"><button data-copy="export DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=sk-...">Copy</button>export DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=sk-...</pre>
      <p><span class="l-en">Your code goes to your machine and the model — nowhere else. Persistent options live in the <a href="#configfile">config file</a>.</span><span class="l-zh">你的代码只会经过你的机器与模型,不去任何别处。持久化选项见<a href="#configfile">配置文件</a>。</span></p>

      <h2 id="cache"><span class="l-en">Prefix cache</span><span class="l-zh">前缀缓存</span></h2>
      <p><span class="l-en">DeepSeek bills cached prefix tokens at a fraction of fresh computation. Most agents waste this: they reorder messages, rewrite summaries mid-session, or inject volatile timestamps — every change invalidates the cache from that point on.</span><span class="l-zh">DeepSeek 对缓存前缀 token 的计费远低于新计算。多数智能体浪费了这一点:重排消息、会话中改写摘要、注入易变的时间戳——任何改动都会让其后的缓存全部失效。</span></p>
      <p><span class="l-en">VoltUI serializes context deterministically and keeps a cache-stable prefix. When the provider reports cached-token details, the local usage ledger records cache hit and miss so you can verify the effect instead of relying on a generic claim. See <a href={`${base}/usage/`}>Compute &amp; usage</a>.</span><span class="l-zh">VoltUI 以确定性方式序列化上下文并保持缓存稳定前缀。当模型服务返回缓存 Token 明细时，本地用量账本会记录命中与未命中，让你用真实数据验证效果，而不是依赖笼统承诺。参见<a href={`${base}/usage/`}>算力用量</a>。</span></p>

      <h2 id="permissions"><span class="l-en">Permissions &amp; sandbox</span><span class="l-zh">权限与沙箱</span></h2>
      <p><span class="l-en">Permissions gate each tool call: <code>deny</code> &gt; <code>ask</code> &gt; <code>allow</code> &gt; fallback. Readers always allow; writers fall back to <code>[permissions] mode</code>. <code>voltui chat</code> prompts before each writer; <code>voltui run</code> stays autonomous but still honours <code>deny</code>.</span><span class="l-zh">权限逐个把关工具调用:<code>deny</code> &gt; <code>ask</code> &gt; <code>allow</code> &gt; 兜底。读工具始终放行;写工具回退到 <code>[permissions] mode</code>。<code>voltui chat</code> 在每次写操作前询问;<code>voltui run</code> 自主运行,但仍遵守 <code>deny</code>。</span></p>
      <p><span class="l-en">The sandbox is enforcement: file-writers refuse any path outside <code>[sandbox] workspace_root</code> (default: the current dir), resolving symlinks and <code>..</code> so a link can't tunnel out. Reads are unrestricted.</span><span class="l-zh">沙箱负责强制执行:写文件工具拒绝 <code>[sandbox] workspace_root</code>(默认当前目录)之外的任何路径,并解析符号链接与 <code>..</code>,防止借链接逃逸。读取不受限。</span></p>

      <h2 id="mcp"><span class="l-en">Plugins (MCP)</span><span class="l-zh">插件(MCP)</span></h2>
      <p><span class="l-en">VoltUI is an MCP client. A <code>[[plugins]]</code> entry's <code>type</code> selects the transport — <code>stdio</code> (default) launches a local subprocess, <code>http</code> connects to a remote <code>url</code>. Tools surface to the model as <code>mcp__&lt;server&gt;__&lt;tool&gt;</code>. Already have an <code>.mcp.json</code>? Drop it in the project root and VoltUI reads it as-is.</span><span class="l-zh">VoltUI 是一个 MCP 客户端。<code>[[plugins]]</code> 条目的 <code>type</code> 选择传输方式——<code>stdio</code>(默认)启动本地子进程,<code>http</code> 连接远程 <code>url</code>。工具以 <code>mcp__&lt;server&gt;__&lt;tool&gt;</code> 呈现给模型。已有 <code>.mcp.json</code>?放到项目根目录,VoltUI 会原样读取。</span></p>
      <pre class="codeblock"><span class="c"># voltui.toml</span>
[[plugins]]                       <span class="c"># local stdio server</span>
name    = "example"
command = "voltui-plugin-example"

[[plugins]]                       <span class="c"># remote server over Streamable HTTP</span>
name    = "stripe"
type    = "http"
url     = "https://mcp.stripe.com"
headers = &#123; Authorization = "Bearer $&#123;STRIPE_KEY&#125;" &#125;</pre>

      <h2 id="cli"><span class="l-en">CLI &amp; slash commands</span><span class="l-zh">命令行与斜杠命令</span></h2>
      <pre class="codeblock">voltui setup              <span class="c"># first-run: pick provider + keys</span>
voltui code               <span class="c"># start an interactive session in the current repo</span>
voltui chat               <span class="c"># interactive session, prompts before writes</span>
voltui run "&lt;task&gt;"       <span class="c"># autonomous run, honours deny rules</span></pre>
      <p><span class="l-en">Inside a session, slash commands run locally — <code>/help</code> lists them all:</span><span class="l-zh">会话中,斜杠命令在本地运行——<code>/help</code> 列出全部:</span></p>
      <pre class="codeblock">/compact   /new      /rewind   /tree     /branch
/switch    /todo     /model    /mcp      /skills
/hooks     /memory   /language /output-style       /help</pre>
      <p><span class="l-en"><code>/branch [name]</code> forks the current conversation tip, <code>/switch &lt;id|name&gt;</code> loads another branch. Custom commands are Markdown files under <code>.voltui/commands/</code>.</span><span class="l-zh"><code>/branch [name]</code> 从当前会话尖端分叉,<code>/switch &lt;id|name&gt;</code> 加载另一条分支。自定义命令是 <code>.voltui/commands/</code> 下的 Markdown 文件。</span></p>

      <h2 id="usage"><span class="l-en">Usage report</span><span class="l-zh">用量报表</span></h2>
      <p><span class="l-en">Usage events are appended to a local, content-free JSONL ledger. The report can group requests, token totals, cache hit/miss, reasoning tokens and estimated cost by day, model, source and product surface.</span><span class="l-zh">用量事件会追加到本地、不含会话内容的 JSONL 账本中。报表可以按天、模型、来源和产品入口聚合请求数、Token、缓存命中/未命中、推理 Token 与预估成本。</span></p>
      <pre class="codeblock"><button data-copy="voltui usage --since 30d">Copy</button>voltui usage --since 30d
voltui usage --json</pre>
      <div class="callout"><span class="ico">i</span><span><span class="l-en">This is model-call accounting, not GPU or cluster monitoring. VoltUI does not claim VRAM, node-health or centralized team-quota visibility today.</span><span class="l-zh">这是模型调用用量账本，不是 GPU 或集群监控。VoltUI 当前不宣称提供显存、节点健康或中心化团队配额能力。</span></span></div>

      <h2 id="configfile"><span class="l-en">Config file</span><span class="l-zh">配置文件</span></h2>
      <p><span class="l-en">Resolution order: flag &gt; <code>./voltui.toml</code> &gt; <code>~/.voltui/config.toml</code> &gt; built-in defaults. Legacy config paths are still migrated when found.</span><span class="l-zh">解析顺序：flag &gt; <code>./voltui.toml</code> &gt; <code>~/.voltui/config.toml</code> &gt; 内置默认值。发现旧配置路径时仍会迁移加载。</span></p>
      <pre class="codeblock"><span class="c"># ~/.voltui/config.toml</span>
default_model = "deepseek-flash"

[agent]
auto_plan = "ask"                  <span class="c"># off|ask|on</span>

[[providers]]
name        = "deepseek-flash"
kind        = "openai"
base_url    = "https://api.deepseek.com"
model       = "deepseek-v4-flash"
api_key_env = "DEEPSEEK_API_KEY"

[permissions]
mode  = "ask"                                <span class="c"># ask|allow|deny</span>
deny  = ["bash(rm -rf*)", "bash(git push*)"]
allow = ["bash(go test*)"]</pre>
      <p><span class="l-en">For the full schema and every field's contract, see <a href={`${repo}/blob/main/docs/SPEC.md`}>SPEC.md §5</a>.</span><span class="l-zh">完整 schema 与每个字段的契约见 <a href={`${repo}/blob/main/docs/SPEC.md`}>SPEC.md §5</a>。</span></p>

      <div class="doc-cards">
        <a class="doc-card" href={`${base}/usage/`}>
          <h3><span class="l-en">Inspect compute usage →</span><span class="l-zh">查看算力用量 →</span></h3>
          <p><span class="l-en">Understand the local ledger, cost model and current measurement boundary.</span><span class="l-zh">了解本地账本、成本模型和当前测量边界。</span></p>
        </a>
        <a class="doc-card" href={repo}>
          <h3><span class="l-en">Contribute →</span><span class="l-zh">参与贡献 →</span></h3>
          <p><span class="l-en">VoltUI is MIT-licensed and open source — good first issues are waiting.</span><span class="l-zh">VoltUI 采用 MIT 许可、开源——新手友好任务等着你。</span></p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>

  <SiteFooter />
</Base>
